        "If a balance between community benefits and efficient project delivery is achieved alongside accelerated EPBC assessments, Central Queensland will be able to generate the renewable electricity needed to electrify existing industries and establish new ones for green exports. Reinvigorated REZ development could help overcome these barriers by providing a framework for coordinated project connections, EPBC approvals, strategic land-use planning and community and regional benefits.",
